{"data": [{"id": "4743733", "title": "Ashtead Group: Near-Term Performance Is Uncertain, But Upside Remains Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='A Sunbelt Rentals aerial lift against a clear blue sky. The green and white lift platform is raised high, indicating it\"s ready for use in construction.' data-id=\"2155939559\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Marvin Samuel Tolentino Pineda</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4721636-ashtead-group-expecting-ebitda-to-continue-growing-in-the-coming-years\">my coverage</a> on Ashtead Group (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASHTF\" title=\"Ashtead Group plc\">OTCPK:ASHTF</a>) (aka AHT) in Sep\u201924, which I recommended a buy rating due to my expectation that the business will continue to see growth recovery when the macro environment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155939559/image_2155939559.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743733-ashtead-group-stock-q2-near-term-performance-uncertain-but-upside-remains-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:59:03"}, {"id": "4743732", "title": "PDD Holdings: Great Business, Big Potential, Low Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pinduoduo and Temu app icon. Both belong to Chinese e-commerce company PDD Holdings\" data-id=\"1865685449\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Robert Way</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Context</strong></h2> <p>In the context of China\u2019s 36-months long-running bear market, PDD Holdings Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PDD\" title=\"PDD Holdings Inc.\">PDD</a></span>) formerly known as Pinduoduo, has seen its stock price decrease by 50% since its peak in February 2021 despite outstanding operational performance. As we will</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865685449/image_1865685449.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743732-pdd-holdings-inc-great-business-big-potential-low-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:51:10"}, {"id": "4743731", "title": "PBDC: A Diversified BDC Choice", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ETF - Exchange Traded Funds\" data-id=\"1706231587\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"538px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Torsten Asmus</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Putnam BDC Income ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PBDC\" title=\"Putnam BDC Income ETF\">PBDC</a></span>) </strong>is a business development company-oriented exchange-traded fund whose portfolio includes the biggest BDCs in the sector.</p> <p>The Putnam BDC Income ETF offers passive income investors the opportunity to mitigate stock-specific risks by presenting a diversified</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743731-pbdc-etf-diversified-bdc-choice", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:43:39"}, {"id": "4743730", "title": "Ollie's Bargain Outlet: Robust Performance Deserves A Premium Multiple (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Florist Putting Cash In His Register\" data-id=\"1135796956\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tom Werner/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment action</h2> <p>I recommended a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720705-ollies-bargain-outlet-rating-downgrade-as-upside-is-no-longer-attractive\">hold rating</a> for Ollie\u2019s Bargain Outlet (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OLLI\" title=\"Ollie's Bargain Outlet Holdings, Inc.\">OLLI</a></span>) when I wrote about it on 12<sup>th</sup> September as valuation has caught up with my previous price target. Based</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135796956/image_1135796956.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743730-ollies-bargain-outlet-stock-robust-performance-deserves-premium-multiple", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:22:35"}, {"id": "4743729", "title": "Kforce: Betting On A Robust Labor Market Recovery", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesswomen meeting in modern conference room\" data-id=\"2155192264\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong> </strong></h2> <h2><strong>Investment Thesis</strong></h2> <p>I believe that Kforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KFRC\" title=\"Kforce Inc.\">KFRC</a></span>) is a strong buy, and I expect its share price to exceed $85 in the coming 12 months (~40% return). The stock price has fallen from its 2021 highs (above $80) to the current $60 level due to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192264/image_2155192264.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743729-kforce-betting-on-a-robust-labor-market-recovery", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:19:09"}, {"id": "4743728", "title": "EQWL: A Low-Valuation Equal-Weight ETF, Outperforming Peers But Lagging The S&P 500 Index", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"New York Stock Exchange Building\" data-id=\"1042838398\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ivan Chertok</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Funds using an equal-weight approach come out as an interesting option to diversify risk and mitigate excess volatility, as this allocation structure helps avoid stock concentration in an environment where the stock market gains have significantly increased the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1042838398/image_1042838398.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743728-eqwl-low-valuation-equal-weight-etf-outperforming-peers-but-lagging-sp500-index", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 05:06:46"}, {"id": "4743726", "title": "Consumer Price Index: Inflation Edges Up To 2.75% In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with CPI word and stack of coins and increasing graph with shopping cart icon. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth\" data-id=\"2078053280\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ratana21</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Jennifer Nash</em></p> <p>Inflation rose slightly in November. According to the Bureau of Labor Statistics, the headline figure for the Consumer Price Index rose to 2.75% year-over-year, right in line with economist expectations.</p> <p>Additionally, core CPI came in at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743726-consumer-price-index-inflation-edges-up-to-2-75-percent-in-november", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 03:30:00"}, {"id": "4743721", "title": "Phathom Pharmaceuticals: The Large Drop Is, Well, Unfathomable", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Failure Concept\" data-id=\"1726514483\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1726514483/image_1726514483.jpg?io=getty-c-w320